<https://w3id.org/perkonto#Email> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An individual email message exchanged between researchers.  Serves as the provenance anchor for all knowledge triples extracted into  PERK. Every relationship carries a source property referencing one or  more Email instances."@en .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#Email> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Email"@en .
