<https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperBib> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A bibliographic metadata record for a published paper,  capturing identifiers, venue, and publication details."@en .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperBib> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Paper Bibliographic Record"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperStatus
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperStatus> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A node representing a single state in the submission  lifecycle of a paper (e.g. Submitted, Under Review, Revision Required,  Accepted, Rejected). Status nodes are chained via movesTo to encode  the full submission history."@en .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#PaperStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Paper Status"@en .
# 
