<https://w3id.org/perkonto#Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A researcher or collaborator appearing as sender, recipient,  or named entity in the email corpus."@en .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Person"@en .
# 
