<https://w3id.org/perkonto#SubmissionID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A composite identifier linking a specific paper to a  specific submission instance at a target venue, enabling tracking of  multiple parallel or sequential submissions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#SubmissionID> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Submission ID"@en .
