<https://w3id.org/perkonto#Task> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A research task or problem formulation that datasets,  methods, or metrics are applied to."@en .
<https://w3id.org/perkonto#Task> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Task"@en .
